Package: sautobuild
Architecture: any
Depends: sbuild, ruby, ruby1.8, dpkg-dev, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: ubuntu-dev-tools
Description: This automatically builds Debian packages for all available architectures
 This is the logical extension of sbuild, for use when building a package for
 multiple architectures.  It also creates a basic Debian package repository,
 for your new packages, as required.
